page.title: 20LEWES HELP FOR THE PROJECT
page.content: This block has been compiled by{all {the first-year pupils of Lewes Priory {School.}They have all spent several weeks of Geography lessons in close examination of their town. They could not have done this without the kind co-operation of many Lewesians, and a few are listed below, with grateful thanks for their time and patience. {T.Reeves Mr.Masters J.Houghton Moss's {Baxters, Clothkits Safeways Parsons B. {Telecom, Lunnons, Gosnells Culverwells {Corona Caffyns, Harveys Hill,Norman & {Beard, Cutform,Robinson's Farm Boeh- {ringers P.C.Lloyd, J.Etherington. {IN SCHOOL: D.Heppenstall + 2DH, V. {Williams,J.Evans,P.Bristow,P.Aldridge, {M.Burgan,R.Gilmore.}And many firms, parents and anonymous Lewesians inter- viewed in the town. And my thanks to all,as co-ordinator {ELIZABETH AMBROSE, PRIORY GEOG. DEPT.
